c: 10
v: 3
t: "Toto Nyasaye wenyu ni wulia owaloonga likulu nende eshialo khu tsinyanga tsisaasaba, mana naleng’aana khushisala (Arsh), Ye niye ubusinjia amakhuwa koosi, abulaho ulisabila owundi yesi yesi Ye nalamuchamile tawe. Oyo niye Nyasaye, omulesi wenyu, kho mumulaame Ye, koo shimwitsulilanga tawe"